<h1 class="fw-bold mb-3" style="color:#F9FAFB;font-size:1.5rem;">Privacy Policy</h1>
<div style="color:#94A3B8;font-size:0.9rem;line-height:1.7;">
    <p>Resume AI processes uploaded resumes solely for screening analysis. No resume data is stored, shared, or used for training beyond the current session.</p>
    <p class="mt-3">Uploaded documents are processed in-memory and discarded after analysis. We do not retain, sell, or distribute any personal information extracted from resumes.</p>
</div>
